            </div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="dfeuk-grid-column-one-third dfeuk-card-group__item">
          <div class="dfeuk-card dfeuk-card--clickable">
            <div class="dfeuk-card__content">
              <h2 class="dfeuk-card__heading dfeuk-heading-m"><a href="/community">Community</a></h2>
              <p class="dfeuk-card__description">Communities of Practice and professions in DfE</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="dfeuk-grid-column-one-third dfeuk-card-group__item">
          <div class="dfeuk-card dfeuk-card--clickable">
            <div class="dfeuk-card__content">
              <h2 class="dfeuk-card__heading dfeuk-heading-m"><a href="/design-ops">Design Ops</a></h2>
              <p class="dfeuk-card__description">How the Design Operations team support design professions in DfE</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <hr class="dfeuk-u-margin-top-2 dfeuk-u-margin-bottom-6">
      <div class="dfeuk-grid-row">
        <div class="dfeuk-grid-column-two-thirds">

          <h2>Support</h2>
          <p>The manual is maintained by the <a href="/design-ops">Design Ops team</a>. If you've got a question or want to feedback, you can <a href="/design-ops/contact">get in touch</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  </main>

